snippet.title: Rocky Super-Action Boxing - ColecoVision Boxing Game (Coleco 1983)
snippet.description:
The history of the ColecoVision is a knockout at The Dot Eaters:
http://thedoteaters.com/?bitstory=colecovision

Rocky Balboa and Clubber Lang duke it out in Rocky Super-Action Boxing,  a fine ColecoVision  boxing game.

-~-~~-~~~-~~-~-
View the goofy glitch that makes playing Access Software's classic game Leader Board Golf so much fun: 
https://youtu.be/HnEN942x5rY
-~-~~-~~~-~~-~-
